				<p><strong>Looking for a new way to engage your employees or customers?</strong> Fortune 500 companies and leading foundations including Google, TripAdvisor and Hewlett-Packard Company Foundation have used our customizable engagement program to reconnect with their employees and customers by giving them the opportunity to choose which borrowers to support. Repayments return to your corporate account and tax-advantaged lending is also available.</p>

				<p>This investment creates multi-year programming that amplifies your impact and creates a unique customer or employee experience. Contact us at <a href="mailto:development@kiva.org">development@kiva.org</a> to learn more.</p>

				<h2>Benefits of employee and customer engagement programs</h2>
				<div class="checklist"><ul>
					<li>Direct your support to the causes you care most about</li>
					<li>Multiply your impact by activating Kiva lenders</li>
					<li>Detailed data tracking</li>
					<li>Public recognition on Kiva.org</li>
					<li>Tax-deductibility if contributing at least $50,000</li>
				</ul></div>

